{"tid":2079593,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一個男人喊住同你講分手 仲愛唔愛你？","createTime":"2020-06-26T01:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T21:50:59.000Z","uid":254339,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b88cce188b977951e6c91341722bf01206c4610b","tid":2079593,"uid":254339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"之前一直都好地地 <br />\n但佢最近做野好忙 好大壓力<br />\n最近哩一兩日好冷淡 然後突然就話要分手 <br />\n<br />\n佢話我地理念 目標 生活習慣都唔同 <br />\n雖然我覺得我同佢之間有d位的確係有分歧 <br />\n但唔係d價值觀/原則性嘅大問題<br />\n比較多係大家生活習慣 愛好問題 <br />\n<br />\n佢一路講 我地大家都一齊喊 <br />\n我係佢面前 雖然都有喊 但表現得好冷靜 <br />\n返到屋企 個心先真係好似裂開左咁<br />\n喊左7個鐘無停過 <br />\n個頭 眼 頸 都喊到好痛 咩都無食但仲嘔埋出黎 <br />\n<br />\n我好愛佢 <br />\n係咪無得挽回？"},{"pid":"ce437e7808d100ec85c0bbfecc591fdc41913f3d","tid":2079593,"uid":101985,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:42:11.000Z","msg":"藉口，有第二條女"},{"pid":"9893c89dffe91c0415463bc2076cb9425cfff3ab","tid":2079593,"uid":76945,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:42:36.000Z","msg":"下 咁突然喊住講分手？你有冇問清楚咩事先呀？"},{"pid":"9cc5c1a78ddf56a9544fbd064d8805b3e9ac9371","tid":2079593,"uid":254339,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"ce437e7808d100ec85c0bbfecc591fdc41913f3d","tid":2079593,"uid":101985,"like":43,"dislike":3,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:42:11.000Z","msg":"藉口，有第二條女"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:43:19.000Z","msg":"佢最近返工好忙, 我都幾肯定無"},{"pid":"9224a48cec684d48ed9cdd4670300048a903109a","tid":2079593,"uid":242998,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:44:40.000Z","msg":"可能人地真係鍾意女人呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994d66c1747954faacb80b422f4c82a2ef46c440","tid":2079593,"uid":61447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b88cce188b977951e6c91341722bf01206c4610b","tid":2079593,"uid":254339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"之前一直都好地地 <br />\n但佢最近做野